steps.name: I open the Legacy file and retrieve the legacy overtime hours data for employee with EmployeeID
I log into the OrangeHRM application
I locate the overtime hours data for employee with EmployeeID in the web application
I compare the overtime data between the legacy system and the web application for employee with EmployeeID
I take a screenshot of the page and save it
I update the "Comparison.xlsx" file with the comparison results for employee with EmployeeID in the Comment section, including the screenshot file name
I log out from the OrangeHRM application
